Package: soildiv
Type: Package
Title: Soil Diversity Calculations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Brennan", "Bean", email = "brennan.bean@usu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package streamlines the process for estimating soil diversity
    metrics. The functions assume that pixel counts are provided as columns 
    connected with a single polygon GEOID. 
